{"slug":"sirkuler-25-0069eng","reference":"Sirkuler_25_0069ENG","gazette":"Official Gazette Dated 31 December 2024 and Numbered 32769 3. Duplicate","title":"The Communiqué on the Import of Certain Electric and Externally Rechargeable Hybrid Vehicles (Import: 2025/7), which regulates the import of Electric Vehicles, has been published","date":"13 Ocak 2025","bodyHtml":"<p><a href=\"https://www.resmigazete.gov.tr/eskiler/2024/12/20241231M3-11.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration-line: underline; font-weight: bold;\">The Communiqué on the Import of Certain Electric and Externally Rechargeable Hybrid Vehicles (Import: 2025/7),</a> which regulates the import of electric or externally rechargeable hybrid vehicles subject to type approval, has been published.</p><p>The Communiqué No. 2024/22, which regulates the implementation of 2024, has been repealed.</p><p>As it is known, if the goods within the scope of the Communiqué are not originating in the European Union and countries with which a Free Trade Agreement has been signed,&nbsp; a \"Permit Certificate\" issued by the customs administrations, the Ministry of Industry and Technology or the institution or organization authorized by it is sought in the registration of customs declarations&nbsp;if they are subject to the Free Movement Regime &nbsp;In order to be exempt from the permit, the goods must come with a A.TR Movement Certificate or a proof of origin certificate within the scope of the relevant Free Trade Agreement.</p><p>The Communiqué No. 2025/7 expanded the scope of goods subject to the Electric Vehicle Import Permit.</p><p>The table of goods within the scope of the Communiqué has been changed as follows.</p><table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"left\" width=\"98%\" style=\"width:98.42%;mso-cellspacing:0cm;background:white;\r\n mso-yfti-tbllook:1184;mso-table-lspace:7.05pt;margin-left:4.8pt;mso-table-rspace:\r\n 7.05pt;margin-right:4.8pt;mso-table-anchor-vertical:paragraph;mso-table-anchor-horizontal:\r\n column;mso-table-left:left;mso-table-top:-10.8pt;mso-padding-alt:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\">\r\n <tbody><tr>\r\n  <td width=\"12%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:12.64%;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">HS CODE</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"43%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:43.68%;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Description of the Item (only electric\r\n  vehicles or externally rechargeable hybrids)</span></b><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"43%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:43.68%;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">CHANGE</span></b><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n <tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:1;height:85.15pt\">\r\n  <td width=\"12%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:12.64%;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\r\n  height:85.15pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">8701.21</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">8701.22</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">8701.23</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">8701.24</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">8701.29</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"43%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:43.68%;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\r\n  height:85.15pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Tow trucks for semi-trailers</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"43%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:43.68%;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\r\n  height:85.15pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">NEW ADDED</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n <tr>\r\n  <td width=\"12%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:12.64%;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">8701.91.10</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">8701.92.10</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">8701.93.10</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">8701.94.10</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">8701.95.10</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"43%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:43.68%;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Wheeled agricultural tractors\r\n  and wheeled tractors used in forestry</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"43%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:43.68%;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">NEW ADDED</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n <tr>\r\n  <td width=\"12%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:12.64%;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">8702</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"43%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:43.68%;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Motor vehicles for the transport\r\n  of 10 or more persons (including the driver)</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"43%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:43.68%;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">NEW ADDED</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n <tr>\r\n  <td width=\"12%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:12.64%;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">8703</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"43%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:43.68%;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Passenger cars and other motor\r\n  vehicles (except those falling under heading 87.02) (except go-kart\r\n  vehicles)(except for tracked vehicles for rescue/emergency response purposes\r\n  with HS 8703.10.11.00.00) (including station wagons and racing cars)</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"43%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:43.68%;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">All positions classified under\r\n  heading 8703 are classified only as electric or externally rechargeable\r\n  hybrids (except go-kart vehicles) (except for tracked vehicles for\r\n  rescue/emergency response purposes with 8703.10.11.00.00)</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n <tr>\r\n  <td width=\"12%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:12.64%;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">8704</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"43%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:43.68%;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Motor vehicles for the transport\r\n  of goods</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"43%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:43.68%;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">All vehicles classified under\r\n  heading 8704, electric only or externally rechargeable hybrids, were covered\r\n  without distinction between new and used</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n <tr>\r\n  <td width=\"12%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:12.64%;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">8705</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"43%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:43.68%;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Special-purpose motor vehicles\r\n  (other than those specially built to transport people or goods) (eg;\r\n  rescuers, crane vehicles, fire trucks, concrete mixer vehicles, road sweeping\r\n  cars, spraying cars, mobile workshops, mobile radiology units)</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"43%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:43.68%;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">NEW ADDED</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n <tr>\r\n  <td width=\"12%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:12.64%;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">8711</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"43%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:43.68%;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Motorcycles (including mopeds)\r\n  and wheeled vehicles with an auxiliary motor (with or without sidecars);\r\n  Baskets</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"43%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:43.68%;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">NEW ADDED</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n <tr>\r\n  <td width=\"12%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:12.64%;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">8716</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"43%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:43.68%;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color: black;\">Trailers and semi-trailers;\r\n  other vehicles </span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">not mechanically propelled</span><span style=\"color: black;\">; components and parts thereof\r\n  (</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Except&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black;\">8716.80;&nbsp; 8716.90)</span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"43%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:43.68%;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">NEW ADDED</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">(8716.80 and&nbsp; 8716.90&nbsp; are exempted)</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n</tbody></table><p><br></p><p>Changes have also been made to the conditions required for the issuance of a Permit Certificate;</p><p>- For T-class motor vehicles defined in the Road Traffic Regulation, it will be necessary to certify by the Turkish Standards Institute (TSE) that the authorized service station has been established by the importer in TS 12047 and TSE K 646 standards</p><p>- The manufacturer of the goods to be imported will need to have an authorized representative residing in the country</p><p>Application on January 1, 2025 for vehicles in tariff position 8703 and 8704; for other products, it will enter into force on March 1, 2025.</p><div><br></div><div><br></div>\n                                <a target=\"_blank\" class=\"text-danger\" href=\"\">\n                                    \n                                </a>"}
